channel.title: Moparscape aint working!
channel.description: Well, heres what happened. I was playing moparscape for like a couple of weeks then I tryed to connect to a server and it would'nt work! So I tried the new java and it still did not work. I don't know whats the matter with it but I cant download the client b/c my comp cannot handle it. PLZ HELP!!!

item.title: Moparscape aint working!
item.dc:creator: @Verac Verac
item.description:
@Verac wrote:

um an error message would be nice b/c i have no idea whats going on, if its the webclient like in an above post the server may be down but i use the dowloaded client so yea, and if its something with Java download the newest java and i got an error claiming i was missing a file titled “Main Class” i found it on my main computer but couldnt transfer it but downloading JDK v 6.3 fixed it. Hope i helped or steered you in the right direction…
